edu.umn.nlpengine

Class LabelIndex.DefaultImpls

  • edu.umn.nlpengine.LabelIndex.DefaultImpls
  • Enclosing interface:
    LabelIndex<T extends Label>

    public static class LabelIndex.DefaultImpls

    A collection of labels ordered by their location in text. By default sorts by ascending TextRange.getStartIndex and then ascending TextRange.getEndIndex.

    See Also:
    TextRange.getStartIndex, TextRange.getEndIndex
